==概念和創作==
《最終幻想VI》是該系列第一部角色設計是除了[[天野喜孝|天野喜孝]]外還有多名設計師，而角色和怪物圖形[[野村哲也|野村哲也]]也創作了原始設計，包括許多故事情節和西傑亞·希吉爾斯<ref name="EdgeMaking">{{cite web|url=http://www.edge-online.com/features/the-making-of-final-fantasy-vi/#null|title=The Making Of: Final Fantasy VI|author=Edge Staff|publisher=Edge Magazine|date=August 5, 2013|accessdate=09-08-2013|archive-date=2013-12-11|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20131211080259/http://www.edge-online.com/features/the-making-of-final-fantasy-vi/#null|dead-url=no}}</ref>，場景設計[[嵯峨空哉|嵯峨空哉]]的設計還有艾德加·羅尼·菲加洛和馬修·羅尼·菲加洛<ref>[http://www.siliconera.com/2010/06/04/reflections-with-soraya-saga-part-1/ Reflections With Soraya Saga Part 1 // Siliconera] {{Wayback|url=http://www.siliconera.com/2010/06/04/reflections-with-soraya-saga-part-1/ |date=20160312012030 }}. Siliconera.com (2010-06-04). Retrieved on 2011-01-16.</ref>。聯合總監Kitase想創造盡可能多的字符，使故事沒有圍繞著一個角色（主角）旋轉<ref name="1up.com">[http://www.1up.com/do/feature?pager.offset=2&cId=3178085 Final Fantasy: Kitase's Inside Story from] {{Webarchive|url=https://archive.is/20130110162531/http://www.1up.com/do/feature?pager.offset=2&cId=3178085 |date=2013-01-10 }}. 1UP.com. Retrieved on 2011-01-16.</ref>。

